OL,3,CPoliticians react to MET police
OL,4,Cinvestigation of China spy claims
OL,6,FPoliticians have been reacting to the
OL,7,Fnews that three men with previous
OL,8,Flinks to welsh politics have been
OL,9,Farrested in Wales and London on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of spying for China and
OL,11,F"targeting UK democracy".
OL,13,FAll three were bailed this morning,
OL,14,Fand searches have been carried out at
OL,15,Fthe addresses where they were
OL,16,Farrested, the Metropolitan Police said.
OL,18,FThe trio, who have previously advised
OL,19,FWelsh Labour politicians, are Matthew
OL,20,FAplin, 43, Steve Jones, 68, and David
OL,21,FTaylor, 39.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@XO]
