OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1772885578
OL,3,CPoliticians react to MET police
OL,4,Cinvestigation of China spy claims
OL,6,FMr Taylor is the husband of Scottish
OL,7,FLabour MP Joani Reid. In her statement
OL,8,Fafter the arrests, Ms Reid said: "I
OL,9,Fhave never been to China. I have never
OL,10,Fspoken on China or China-related
OL,11,Fmatters in the Commons. I have never
OL,12,Fasked a question on China-related
OL,13,Fmatters.''
OL,15,FSteve Jones is a former special
OL,16,Fadviser to the Welsh Government.
OL,17,FMatthew Aplin was a press officer for
OL,18,FLabour Senedd members and David Taylor
OL,19,Fis a former special adviser to the UK
OL,20,FGovernment.
OL,26,@pD@bOU
