OL,3,CPoliticians react to MET police
OL,4,Cinvestigation of China spy claims
OL,6,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan said: "I
OL,7,Fam aware of three arrests that took
OL,8,Fplace yesterday as part of a counter-
OL,9,Fterrorism policing investigation. The
OL,10,Findividuals were arrested on suspected
OL,11,Foffences under the National Security
OL,12,FAct 2023 and have now been released on
OL,13,Fbail.''
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
