CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1772885578
OL,3,CPoliticians react to MET police
OL,4,Cinvestigation of China spy claims
OL,6,F"These are serious allegations and it
OL,7,Fis vital that we do not hamper the
OL,8,Fwork of the police in any way or
OL,9,Fprejudice any future legal process. As
OL,10,Fthis remains a live police
OL,11,Finvestigation, it would be
OL,12,Finappropriate for me to comment
OL,13,Ffurther on any aspect of this case."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
