OL,3,CPoliticians react to MET police
OL,4,Cinvestigation of China spy claims
OL,6,FAlex Norris, Border Security and
OL,7,FAsylum Minister said "We've already
OL,8,Fbeen in contact with Beijing and the
OL,9,FChinese Assembly to register our
OL,10,Fconcern in this area. We are very
OL,11,Fclear: this investigation needs to
OL,12,Ftake its full course. Then we'll
OL,13,Festablish the facts."
OL,15,FOther party's have been commenting
OL,16,Ftoday. Speaking at his party's
OL,17,Fmanifesto launch in Newport Reform UK
OL,18,Fleader Nigel Farage claimed corruption
OL,19,Fwithin the Labour Party "runs deep"
OL,26,@oD@VOUuD@UO]
