OL,3,CPoliticians react to MET police
OL,4,Cinvestigation of China spy claims
OL,6,FHe initially rejected claims that one
OL,7,Fof those who'd been arrested was a
OL,8,FReform member.
OL,10,FHowever, the party's Welsh leader Dan
OL,11,FThomas, later confirmed to ITV Wales
OL,12,Fthat Matthew Aplin was in fact a
OL,13,Fformer member.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
