OL,3,CPoliticians react to MET police
OL,4,Cinvestigation of China spy claims
OL,6,FElsewhere, former security minister
OL,7,Fand Conservative Tom Tugendhat said
OL,8,F''We've had warning after warning on
OL,9,Fthis. The Chinese Government has
OL,10,Fdemonstrated again and again it's
OL,11,Fbehaving like a hostile power,
OL,12,Fintimidating people on our street,
OL,13,Fspying on our Parliament, and trying
OL,14,Fto corrupt individuals.''
